<p><strong>Diversity and Inclusion Statement</strong><br />
At Alliance Data, we believe that each individual provides a unique and valuable perspective on how we serve our clients, drive our business , and engage in our communities. It is our intent to nurture, develop, and utilize these different points of view, encouraging diversity of thought and inclusion of each associate in every aspect of our business.</p>
